    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em>You grew up in wonder of Chelish theater, and spent countless hours in the opera houses across Cheliax and even more time perfecting your voice.</em></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong></p>\n<p>Chelaxian Human Heritage</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Benefits</strong></p>\n<p>You gain a +1 trait bonus on Perform (sing) checks. Furthermore you have memorized the librettos of many works sung in the ancient Azlanti tongue, granting you a +2 trait bonus on Linguistics checks when trying to decipher the ancient Azlanti language.</p>",
